Summary: both objests had 3 large diamond shaped silver/white lights
divs: sighting detailswhile travling north on florida state route 85,5 about 3 to 5 miles north of campton,fl., me and my wife saw a unknown object with 3 large diamon shape (silver\white lighs with slight yellow mist around unknown object).then we saw a second unknown object just like the first one past right in front from 5 to 10 seconds later going in the same direction----east to west. i look over to the west both unknown objects disappeared. i saw no other aircraft in the area at this time,i have seen anything like this before!!!!
